    "Material such as machine documentation, standard work instructions, or issue reports will contain domain jargon and technical information that LLMs may struggle to process.",
    "Furthermore, the text in an issue report may pose additional challenges due to abbreviations, poor grammar, and formatting (Edwards et al., 2008; Oruç, 2020; Müller et al., 2021).",
    "Therefore, as part of this work, we benchmarked several LLMs on their ability to answer questions based on factory manuals and unstructured issue reports.",
